Privacy Policy
Chef Billy's Recipe App
Developed by Dama Finance

Effective Date: 15th June 2023

At Chef Billy's Recipe App, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and disclose information when you use our recipe app. You consent to the practices described in this policy by using Chef Billy's Recipe App.
1. Information We Collect
1.1 Personal Information
We do not require you to provide any personal information to access and use Chef Billy's Recipe App. You can browse our recipe collection and use the app without registering an account or providing any personal details.
1.2 Non-Personal Information
We may collect non-personal information automatically when you access and use Chef Billy's Recipe App. This information may include your device type, IP address, browser information, usage statistics, and other technical details. We may use cookies, web beacons, and similar technologies to collect this information.
2. Use of Information
2.1 Personal Information
Since we do not collect personal information, we do not use it for any purpose.
2.2 Non-Personal Information
We may use non-personal information for the following purposes:
a)	Improve User Experience: We may analyze non-personal information to understand how users interact with Chef Billy's Recipe App and improve its functionality and user interface.
b)	Aggregated Statistics: We may compile non-personal information into aggregated statistics to analyze trends, enhance our services, and share with third parties. These statistics will not contain any personally identifiable information.
c)	Cookies and Analytics: We may use cookies and analytics tools to collect non-personal information and understand user behavior, such as page views, clicks, and session duration. This information helps us improve our app and provide a better user experience.

3. Third-Party Services
Chef Billy's Recipe App may contain links to third-party websites, services, or advertisements. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third parties. We encourage you to review the privacy policies of any third-party services you access through our app.
4. Data Security
We are committed to protecting the security of your information. While we employ industry-standard security measures to safeguard your data, please note that no method of transmission over the Internet or electronic storage is 100% secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security.
5. Children's Privacy
Chef Billy's Recipe App is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we become aware that personal information from a child under 13 has been collected, we will take steps to delete it.
6. Changes to this Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the revised policy on Chef Billy's Recipe App. Your continued use of the app following the posting of changes will constitute your acceptance of those changes.
7. Contact Us
If you have any questions, concerns, or suggestions regarding this Privacy Policy or our practices, please contact us through 
Email: axisgraphics1@gmail.com

Please note that this Privacy Policy only applies to Chef Billy's Recipe App and not to any other services or websites that may be linked to or integrated with our app.

Last updated: 15th June 2023
